{
  "type": "feature",
  "title": "Inline 'Hear corrected version' shadow button on user messages with grammar feedback",
  "description": "Recent iter 640 added an inline 'Shadow this line' button on assistant messages. Mirror that idea on the USER side to close the speaking-feedback loop: when a user's conversation message has grammar feedback containing a corrected sentence (msg.feedback.corrected or similar), render a small inline button under the user bubble that plays the *corrected* version via TTS at slow speed (0.75x) and lets the user shadow it once. This turns each correction into an immediate micro-shadowing drill instead of a passive notice — directly supporting the app's speaking-fluency goal.\n\nImplementation:\n1. Create `frontend/src/components/conversation/CorrectedShadowButton.tsx`: a small button (Volume2 + 'Shadow correction' label) that takes `correctedText: string` and `onShadowComplete?: () => void`. On click, uses `window.speechSynthesis` (rate 0.75) to speak the corrected sentence, shows a 'Listening…' → 'Now repeat' state, then optionally fires onShadowComplete. Reuse the visual style of `InlineShadowButton` for consistency. Disable when text is empty or equals the user's original.\n2. Export it from `frontend/src/components/conversation/index.ts` (or wherever InlineShadowButton is exported).\n3. In `frontend/src/pages/Conversation.tsx`, locate the user-message rendering branch (the one that renders msg.feedback via FeedbackPanel) and render `<CorrectedShadowButton correctedText={msg.feedback.corrected} />` inline beneath the bubble when `msg.role === 'user'` and `msg.feedback?.corrected` exists and differs from `msg.content`. Guard so it only shows once per message.\n4. Add a unit test `frontend/src/__tests__/CorrectedShadowButton.test.tsx` covering: (a) renders when correctedText is non-empty and differs from original, (b) hidden/disabled when correctedText equals original, (c) clicking calls speechSynthesis.speak with rate 0.75 (mock window.speechSynthesis).\n\nNo backend changes; no schema changes. Scope ≤ 4 files.",
  "files_to_modify": [
    "frontend/src/components/conversation/CorrectedShadowButton.tsx",
    "frontend/src/components/conversation/index.ts",
    "frontend/src/pages/Conversation.tsx",
    "frontend/src/__tests__/CorrectedShadowButton.test.tsx"
  ],
  "priority": "high",
  "estimated_complexity": "small"
}
